title: Rasa Imanalijeva
text:
Rasa Imanalijeva is a former <a href="Lithuania">Lithuania</a>n <a href="women%27s%20soccer">football</a> <a href="Striker%20%28association%20football%29">striker</a> and current referee, who played for <a href="Gintra%20Universitetas">Gintra Universitetas</a> in the <a href="A%20Lyga%20%28women%29">A Lyga</a>. She has been the league's top scorer in the 2008, 2009, 2010 and 2011 seasons.
She has been a member of the <a href="Lithuania%20women%27s%20national%20football%20team">Lithuanian national team</a>.
